name: Intending to Return to Afghanistan by end 2005 – Top 24 Districts in Afghanistan, Afghanistan, 2005
description:
Intending to Return to Afghanistan by end 2005 – Top 24
Districts in Afghanistan

Nearly 50% of Afghans in Pakistan who intend to return to Afghanistan by the end of
2005 are from 24 districts in Afghanistan. The top 5 provinces account for more than
21% of total to returns in 2005.
